==========================

This map was originally in Call of Duty and i asked my friend xeno 
(hence the name gg_xeno) if i could transfer his map into css. He said
yes and i made it for css. What i didn't do was post it and the original 
version was deleted once i got a new computer. So here is a remake of the 
original map but better. The basic layout is the same.
==========================

Installation: Put into your cstrike/maps folder.
==========================

Enjoy
